00:28:10,749 --> 00:28:14,131
and it's more than the two big names that everybody thinks of when you think of theme parks.

355
00:28:14,811 --> 00:28:16,252
And as with any creative endeavor,

356
00:28:16,672 --> 00:28:20,394
there are multiple parties who are all working together to make everything happen.

357
00:28:20,434 --> 00:28:25,617
Designers, technicians, programmers, artists, writers, and yes, even managers are needed

358
00:28:27,618 --> 00:28:28,538
to make these things happen.

359
00:28:28,798 --> 00:28:30,039
Somebody has to organize the whole thing.

