380
00:30:42,636 --> 00:30:49,697
So this is what we wanted you to understand, that as storytelling siblings, you should know about us.

381
00:30:49,757 --> 00:30:56,638
This could be a fun little side hustle for you. You might end up with a whole career in theme parks,

382
00:30:56,698 --> 00:30:59,579
or you might end up licensing your game to an attraction.

